Name: Zombie in my city
About the game: This game is developed from the ground up for HTC Vive and it's not game AAA grade. Step in the midst of a low poly zombie apocalypse. Kill them all and save the town where you growing up. Real-life weapon handling: Using VR motion controllers handle over 42 different weapons. Move where you want: using touchpad you can smoothly go there where you wish. Few different game mode: - Throw missions - Street missions - Arena missions (more in next updates)
